line.text: 'Here you can queue up factories and your Architect TL automatically builds them near this Outpost.'
'You can still use the TL as you please. He resumes his Architect task when docked at homebase.'
'Chooses best asteroids. Skips sectors with dangerous enemies. Needs '
'Architect completes orders from bottom to top. Click to remove order. "Free Support" = after that order.'
